Plesk training at Contabo

Contabo is feeling fantastic.
March 25 at 7:20 AM Â·

Do you use Plesk Obsidian already to easily manage your server?
We noticed that the administration panel is becoming more and more popular these days. For quite some time, we offer a free one month trial in combination with every new VPS or dedicated server order.

At the end of January, the experts from Plesk visited us for a training sessions. They had lots of tips and tricks for our colleagues and at the end, everyone received an official Plesk certificate (after completing a Plesk exam)!

Further details can be found in our blog, just click the following link:
